                "category": "interaction",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A cave khefak chews on rock to feed, dealing @Damage[4[piercing]] damage every 10 minutes to the object. This damage ignores 10 points of Hardness. If a khefak doesn't spend at least 1 hour Gnawing Rock per day, it begins to starve until it spends 10 minutes Gnawing Rock.</p>"
